c: 3
v: 103
t: "Jogitee …ďoggol Alla ngol on denndaangal, wata on sertu. JaŇčto…óon Neema Alla on e dow moo…óon nde laatino…óon ayru…ďe, O Woowindiri hakkunde …ďer…óe mon …óen woŇčtir…óon Neema Makko on si…ó…óu…ďe; on laatioke e tonndu ngayka yiite, O Da…óndi on e magge. ko wano nii Alla ∆ĀannginiraŇčta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, bela jo'o, on feeway"